Output docs/demos/demo-grid-topology.gif

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1100
Set Height 650
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 15

Type "# Grid Topology + Power Flow + DR Voltage Regulation"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type ".venv/bin/python3.14 examples/grid_topology_demo.py"
Enter
Sleep 10s

Sleep 3s
